<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 dark:text-white">The Story</h2>
  <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
    <p>From a young age, I've been drawn to the creative process of building things that can have an impact. My journey into software development started as a challenging but rewarding pursuit, where I quickly learned that code is just a means to an end.</p>
    <p>I am a firm believer that design is not just about aesthetics or how it looks. Design is about how it works. My role is to make life easier for developers by creating tools and processes that help them work more efficiently, while keeping the focus on delivering value to our users.</p>
    <p>That mindset has guided dozens of teams I've mentored over the years. I've come to understand that by implementing good practices together with the right tools and processes, we can build software that not only works well but is also maintainable and scalable in the long run.</p>
    <p>Along the road I've been lucky to be part of some great teams and to have had the opportunity to work on some amazing projects. Each one of them has taught me something new and helped shape my philosophy of what makes great software.</p>
  </div>
</section>

